title: Complete Dashboard Confessional Discography - All Albums, Bonus
description:
--==DASHBOARD CONFESSIONAL==--
Proudly presenting all albums, EPs and singles, in high quality MP3.
The albums were ripped from my own personal collection.
The bonus tracks were downloaded elsewhere.

This torrent contains the following albums:

The Swiss Army Romance - 2003 re-release with bonus tracks
The Places You Have Come To Fear The Most
A Mark, A Mission, A Brand, A Scar - With UK bonus tracks
Dusk and Summer - Including hidden track. PLEASE NOTE this contains the SINGLE version of Stolen, sorry I couldn&#039;t find the original, I only have the Special Edition =[
The Shade of Poison Trees
Wire Tapes volume 1

It also contains the following EPs
The Drowning
So Impossible
Summer&#039;s Kiss

And the following bonus tracks:
Warmth of the Sand
Vindicated
Jamie (Weezer Cover)
I Do (RARE)

This is all arranged beautifully in folders (Check Details if you don&#039;t believe me), so download it to your music folder, not your Downloads folder, so you can carry on seeding.

Seed, and please comment.
